# TD bot Telegram / MOTUS

## Step 1 : Create your Bot

connect to Telegram and https://t.me/botfather

generate new bot and get token API : XXXXXXXXXXXX

## create a dedicated nodejs WebApp


We are going to use Telegraf library to handle our telegram bot https://telegraf.js.org/

Target i to have the following behavior with the bot :

- when command start is launch, it will display the word size
- when a word will be send it will be compare to the current word and if len match a status will be return by telegram Bot

tips 
- bot.hears(/(\S+)/, ctx =>{}) allow to get the current input by the user



